**mcp-guide: Project setup available**

This project has not yet been configured for your preferences. Guided onboarding
takes a few minutes and covers:

- Language and framework
- Workflow mode
- Methodology preferences (TDD, SOLID, YAGNI, etc.)
- Testing, code quality, and review posture
- Git operations and commit format
- Style and toolchain

To get started, run:

```
{{@}}guide :onboard
```

Or use the URI: `guide://_onboard`

To skip and configure manually instead:

```
{{@}}guide :onboard --skip
```
